			<td colspan="6" class="DetailTitle" style="text-align:center;">
                            Summary on Grant Application Form</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="6" class="DetailValue" style="padding:5px;">
                        <span id="lblAbstract">This is a proposal to establish at Cardiff a centre for computational spectral theory.  It will be a focus for pure and applied mathematicians and numerical analysis who have an interest in the spectral theory of ODEs and PDEs.  It will draw on multi-disciplinary resources in Universities in Britain, Europe and the USA to achieve synergy. In the first 3 years of its life it will investigate various spectral problems associated with Sturm-Liouville, difference, harmonic and bi-harmonic operators.</span>
                        </td>
		</tr>
